		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I haven't ever played BOF4 (yet ?) so it's not it that inspired this dream.
<br />
<br />However, I think the guillotine part was inspired from Chrono Trigger, and the pig part from Final Fantasy IV where you could be turned into pigs by a spell. Also, this have probably been inspired from The Lord of the Rings, where Frodo and Sam hide themselves as Orcs to intruder the evil lands of Sauron, and had to act like orcs. I read that very long ago so I barely remember a few things.

		

